title: Sat.Cloudy/hot humid (Gardening)(2.5 hrs.)(1000Kcal)(197)
content: 6/2/18: Got up around 8:30 AM and was not planning on doing any exercising, but wife wanted me to take down a tree with vines...and that took a lot longer ans was physically exerting than I imagined. 2.5 hrs later I was sweating and soaked and probably exposed to poison ivy.  I weighed myself after the exercise, 197, used about 1000 kcal.  Washed with Fels Naptha to ward off any immune reaction.
